               <p>258. 
               
                  <persName id="t18010218-48-defend298" type="defendantName">
                     JOHN 
                     ARNOLD
                  <interp inst="t18010218-48-defend298" type="surname" value="ARNOLD"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18010218-48-defend298" type="given" value="JOHN"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18010218-48-defend298" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
               
             was indicted for <rs id="t18010218-48-off264" type="offenceDescription">
                     <interp inst="t18010218-48-off264" type="offenceCategory" value="theft"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18010218-48-off264" type="offenceSubcategory" value="grandLarceny"></interp>
               feloniously stealing, on the <rs id="t18010218-48-cd265" type="crimeDate">19th of January</rs>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18010218-48-off264 t18010218-48-cd265"></join>, two brushes, value 8d. a hammer, value 6d. a pair of gloves, value 6d. a pair of shoes, value 3s. forty yards of broad girth webbing, value 20s. six yards of narrow girth webbing, value 9d. and a quantity of silver, value 3s.
            </rs> the property of 
               
                  <persName id="t18010218-48-victim300" type="victimName">
                     Robert 
                     Lyon
                  <interp inst="t18010218-48-victim300" type="surname" value="Lyon"></interp>
