                     <join result="defendantPunishment" targOrder="Y" targets="t18010218-48-defend298 t18010218-48-punish269"></join>
               Confined six months in the House of Correction
            </rs>.</p>
               <p>First Middlesex Jury, before Mr. Common Serjeant.</p>
